ough each section, placing foils for maximum lift and dimension. After processing, she rinses, tones, and finishes with a treatment and style. The result is polished, bright, and multi-tonal."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoBlock","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Pricing"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"Starting at $250"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoDivider"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoItem","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoLabel","children":"Duration"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__infoValue","children":"3 hr+"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__cta","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"/book","className":"Button-module__zVQJKW__button Button-module__zVQJKW__primary Button-module__zVQJKW__fullWidth","children":"Book This Service"}]}],["$","aside",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__ashleyNote","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteLabel","children":"A note from Ashley"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"page-module__fov6ZW__noteText","children":"Full highlights are a craft. I take my time because even saturation and clean placement are what separate salon blonde from beautiful blonde. Bring a book — we will be here a while, and it will be worth it."}]]}]]}]}],[["$","link","0",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/0~ww8ls-m-185.css","precedence":"next"}],["$","link","1",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/chunks/0u4.swdsoosqq.css","precedence":"next"}],["$","script","script-0",{"src":"/_next/static/chunks/17atglk0iug8t.js","async":true}]],["$","$L3",null,{"children":["$","$4",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@5"}]}]]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"b